<figureCitation id="13210CCCA53265450FD0F665FC9CF8A9" box="[760,824,1837,1861]" captionStart="FIGURES 9–15" captionStartId="2.[151,258,1956,1978]" captionTargetBox="[176,1414,188,1917]" captionTargetId="figure-18@2.[164,1424,182,1931]" captionTargetPageId="2" captionText="FIGURES 9–15. Epimecia (9, 10) and Lophoterges (11–15) spp.: female genitalia. Depositories of specimens: 9, 12–15—BBT; 10— HNHM (photo by V.S. Kononenko); 11—AFM." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4406516" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/4406516/files/figure.png" pageId="0" pageNumber="288">Fig. 9</figureCitation>
) can be distinguished from those of 
<taxonomicName id="4C1A6BCAA53265450992F666FABCF8A9" baseAuthorityName="Freyer" baseAuthorityYear="1835" box="[1210,1304,1837,1861]" class="Insecta" family="Noctuidae" genus="Epimecia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="0" pageNumber="288" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="ustula">
<emphasis id="B96ECC5BA53265450992F666FABCF8A9" box="[1210,1304,1837,1861]" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="288">E. ustula</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(
<figureCitation id="13210CCCA5326545080EF665FAD7F8A9" box="[1318,1395,1837,1861]" captionStart="FIGURES 9–15" captionStartId="2.[151,258,1956,1978]" captionTargetBox="[176,1414,188,1917]" captionTargetId="figure-18@2.[164,1424,182,1931]" captionTargetPageId="2" captionText="FIGURES 9–15. Epimecia (9, 10) and Lophoterges (11–15) spp.: female genitalia. Depositories of specimens: 9, 12–15—BBT; 10— HNHM (photo by V.S. Kononenko); 11—AFM." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4406516" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/4406516/files/figure.png" pageId="0" pageNumber="288">Fig. 10</figureCitation>
) by the more elongated apophyses anteriores and posteriores and conspicuously more elongated sclerotized anterior section of ductus bursae with the anterior bar more strongly extending to the cervix bursae. The female genitalia of the new species are remarkably different from those of the four mentioned 
<taxonomicName id="4C1A6BCAA53265450E28F6D1FC20F85D" authorityName="Hampson" authorityYear="1906" box="[768,900,1945,1969]" class="Insecta" family="Noctuidae" genus="Lophoterges" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="0" pageNumber="288" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
