<typeStatus id="54A1AEEBA53165460FB8F3B4FD1AFCF8" box="[656,702,764,788]" pageId="3" pageNumber="291">type</typeStatus>
locality, vicinity of Tekes village.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
